Package: clashicd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - daemon
 Bitcoin Clashic is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Bitcoin Clashic uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Bitcoin
 Clashic client is the name of the open source software which enables the 
 use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides the daemon, clashicd, and the CLI tool
 clashic-cli to interact with the daemon.

Package: clashic-qt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - Qt GUI
 Bitcoin Clashic is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Bitcoin Clashic uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Bitcoin
 Clashic client is the name of the open source software which enables the
 use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides clashic-qt, a GUI for Bitcoin Clashic based on Qt.

Package: clashic-tx
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer digital currency - standalone transaction tool
 Bitcoin Clashic is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Bitcoin Clashic uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Bitcoin
 Clashic client is the name of the open source software which enables the
 use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides clashic-tx, a command-line transaction creation
 tool which can be used without a bitcoin clashic daemon.  Some means of
 exchanging minimal transaction data with peers is still required.
